def plot_histogram(series):
    fig, ax= plt.subplots(figsize=(9,6))
    sns.distplot(series, ax=ax, hist_kws={'alpha': 0.9, 'edgecolor':'black'},  
        kde_kws={'color': 'black', 'alpha': 0.7})
    sns.despine()
    return fig, ax
